<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lamely" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lamely,</orth> in a halting manner, imperfectly: <cit><quote>l. writ,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 1, 97</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the feet stood l. in the verse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.180" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 180</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so l. and unfashionable,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>their limbs may halt as l. as their manners,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 1, 25</bibl></cit>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>